    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Erase the Deck is a story driven deckbuilder with a scribbling narrator who writes the story. Choose between several cards that can lead to secret endings and decide if you want to follow the narrators instructions or if you want to ignore them. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pick between several cards that can impact the story and combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325120/extras/9f504bdb2a58a8592ea904234b67ff5a.poster.avif?t=1740129488\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325120/extras/9f504bdb2a58a8592ea904234b67ff5a.webm?t=1740129488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325120/extras/9f504bdb2a58a8592ea904234b67ff5a.mp4?t=1740129488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight, spare and do much more with several unique encounters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325120/extras/c080d1887dbc0d21a3a9320f54ee2705.poster.avif?t=1740129488\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325120/extras/c080d1887dbc0d21a3a9320f54ee2705.webm?t=1740129488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ignore the narrators instructions and make terrible choices</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325120/extras/a5532481efd5c10e531ba8931300739a.poster.avif?t=1740129488\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325120/extras/a5532481efd5c10e531ba8931300739a.webm?t=1740129488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A narrator who draws everything</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several unique cards that impact both the story and combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many unique story paths and endings depending on your choices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A bunch of secrets to find</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
